{"tid":362612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家抵制所有二手教科書店","createTime":"2017-08-17T05:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T10:11:13.000Z","uid":29052,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7edbdac50c68e5eb2f695109b4c1eaedf8089729","tid":362612,"uid":29052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:07:05.000Z","msg":"相信大家都知道二手教科書鋪係幾咁無無恥<br />\n大家中學時間都受過二手教科書鋪既壓榨<br />\n<br />\n以下係佢地既罪行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）基本上呢啲時間都會有一堆人企係到不斷r您買書，死狗咁跟住您（明明條街又迫又熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n2）基本上都以一個最平唔合理既價錢收您哂啲書，個本又話唔值錢又盛，結果佢兩三百以內收哂您啲書，而且唔賣仲要死lur爛Lur (試過唔賣都比人屌老母）<br />\n<br />\n3）會一野搶您張書單，然後就直接執書比您迫您買咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住[s[/s]"},{"pid":"065774ded72c4357fddfcbbb55d87a91ee17a81a","tid":362612,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:08:46.000Z","msg":"咁應該咩都唔好買<br />\n新書仲仆街 <br />\n年年話成本上漲 郁下啲圖就叫新版 <br />\n成本下調又唔見佢減下價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3c8df2b5e460ac3499a5c0c4f7d769ef2f44fa","tid":362612,"uid":29052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"另外我地再講下佢地存在既價值!<br />\n係0呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本就無良商人<br />\n<br />\n收收埋埋一堆二三手教科書<br />\n以最高價出售<br />\n而且賣極都係只係得教科書 <br />\n根本對睇書既風氣完全無幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且請埋一堆童工 仲要個制度令到佢地係朋友之間互sell <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (其實幾似傳銷個類）"},{"pid":"ae3fb143d637e606025631ed89aac41fc62e154c","tid":362612,"uid":29052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁應該咩都唔好買<br />\n新書仲仆街 <br />\n年年話成本上漲 郁下啲圖就叫新版 <br />\n成本下調又唔見佢減下價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n既然要比佢呃一筆 點解唔自己放比同學"},{"pid":"b26b747c5e04c677b70461ee984a5e1af21fbcd4","tid":362612,"uid":74085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"支持，果時兩本數學書收得$20，食水勁深"},{"pid":"55ec5d8642ea0f16965c30a424efad6574021d5f","tid":362612,"uid":29781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"其實學校可以自己搞<br />\n同學自己出價比低年級同學買<br />\n咁樣又可以唔駛俾班二手書舖仆街壓榨<br />\n又可以比d學生試下自己做老細 不知幾好<br />\n<br />\n利申:之前學校有搞"},{"pid":"21301d9b5ec01ac864b3cab0481e5bb5b385b1de","tid":362612,"uid":132302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁應該咩都唔好買<br />\n新書仲仆街 <br />\n年年話成本上漲 郁下啲圖就叫新版 <br />\n成本下調又唔見佢減下價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n既然要比佢呃一筆 點解唔自己放比同學</blockquote><br />\n係㗎 其實留畀下届同學係最好&hellip;"},{"pid":"173eebdecf0a9c7f5bed164621d523639594fcfb","tid":362612,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T08:33:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實學校可以自己搞<br />\n同學自己出價比低年級同學買<br />\n咁樣又可以唔駛俾班二手書舖仆街壓榨<br />\n又可以比d學生試下自己做老細 不知幾好<br />\n<br />\n利申:之前學校有搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該推行教育界自編教材，一毫子都唔使俾，先符合九年免費教育精神"},{"pid":"bfc3c9674c361ad39944333c0df95dac14ec9550","tid":362612,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"好人好姐點會去二手教科書店呀"},{"pid":"251f50849723d6d720c6000ab66aea45efb66a04","tid":362612,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:11:13.000Z","msg":